        "content": "<p>Hello, These are methods in .h files which can be accessed through bindgen. How every quite modules have static inline and other methods which are not generated by bindgen. I have given both C options - fkeep-inline-functions and --generate-inline-functions in Rust Makefile. Still no luck. How to access them or what is the approach?</p>",
